# ğŸ† Premier League Match Predictor

This is a simple web-based application that predicts the winner of a Premier League match based on user-selected teams. The prediction is displayed dynamically with a clean interface and themed background.

## ğŸš€ Features

- Dropdowns for selecting two Premier League teams  
- "Predict Winner" button triggers result display  
- Displays predicted winner with styled result text  
- Custom background image support  
- Easily customizable with logos and real stats

